text: JADES-GS-z14-0 is a very far galaxy discovered by the James Webb Space Telescope in 2024. It is the most distant known galaxy from Earth. It was born about 290 million years after the Big Bang. It was discovered as part of the JWST Advanced Deep Extragalactic Survey (JADES) programme. ==References== Category:Galaxies
